```

Skip if Slack MCP unavailable.

## The Golden Rule

**NEVER discard uncommitted changes. If `git status --porcelain` has output, SKIP the slot. Period. No "abandoned" detection, no "orphaned" heuristics, no stashing. ALWAYS verify.**
